title: JNW Makers program
description:
JNW Super Fablab will be conducting its first-ever Makers program with 25  teachers from various schools and volunteer teachers from 7th till 29th July. The program is divided into two parts:

In the first part, the teachers will be trained in using the machines in the lab, and in the second phase will be taking place in August, where students will participate in making projects along with the trained teachers.
